#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc24"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts24"></a>
msgctxt "thag1.24:5.1"
msgid "“Anuvassiko pabbajito,"
msgstr "See the excellence of the teaching!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.24:5.2"
msgid "passa dhammasudhammataṃ;"
msgstr "Just one rainy season after I went forth,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.24:5.3"
msgid "Tisso vijjā anuppattā,"
msgstr "I attained the three knowledges"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.24:5.4"
msgid "kataṃ buddhassa sāsanan”ti."
msgstr "and fulfilled the Buddha’s instructions."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
